membership:
The IRF has ECOSOC status with the United Nations since 1951. IRF is a active partner of World Bank, Interamerican Development Bank, Asian Development Bank and the United Nations offices including the Regional Economic Commissions, the WHO and ILO. We are members of the United Nations Road Safety Collaboration Group (UNRSC) and the World Vehicle Forum. &#xd;
&#xd;
Furthermore, the IRF collaborates with the European Union Road Federation.
